A monster clad in a robe "\N[33]-sama, it seems the Warrior of Light
is approaching us... For now, please return to the gate."

Demon King \N[33]: "Hmm, \N[33], is it... The Warrior of Light, quite
impressive indeed."

Demon King \N[33]: "And what of those two...? Their blunder at their
stronghold is something I cannot simply overlook."

\N[33]: "About that, there are rumors that both of them, fearing
punishment, have vanished without a trace..."

Demon King \N[33]: "What...? Even those who rank among the Three
Generals..."
Demon King \N[33]: "Hmph, well, no matter... I have no use for losers."

\N[33]: "Then, allow me... As one of the Three Generals, I will surely
shatter the Warrior of Light."

Demon King \N[33]: "Huhuhu, I'm looking forward to it. There's only a
little time left until the gate opens... I'm counting on you.
Ah~hahahaha."

A monster clad in a robe "\N[33]sama, it seems the Warriors of Light
are approaching us."

Demon King \N[33]: "\N[33], it seems their stronghold was no good after
all..."

\N[33]: "Yes, the power of the Warriors of Light far exceeds our
imagination. Both Josephine and Loretta have gone missing after their
defeat, and their whereabouts are currently unknown."

Demon King \N[33]: "To think that even the Three Generals... Hmph, so
you fled without even aiding them and shamelessly returned here...?"

\N[33]: "No! I would never... As the Great High Priest of Darkness, I
would not flee."

\N[33]: "Here, I can unleash power close to my true potential. I will
surely defeat them..."

Demon King \N[33]: "Ho ho, then show me you can finish them off here.
The gate will open shortly... Fufufufu, Ah-hahahaha."

A demon clad in a robe "\N[33]-sama, it seems the Warriors of Light
are approaching us."

Demon Lord \N[33]: "\N[33], about the disgrace at their stronghold...
How do you plan to take responsibility?"

Demon Lord \N[33]: "Moreover, you fled without even aiding the other
two...?"

\N[33]: "No...! As one of the three generals and the great dark high
priest, I would never flee..."

\N[33]: "Even if I had fought in that situation, the outcome would
likely have been the same. Such was the overwhelming and formidable
power of the Warriors of Light..."
\N[33]: "But here... Here I can defeat them with my true power!"

Demon Lord \N[33]: "Hmm, then show me you can finish them off here. And
what of the other two...?"

\N[33]: "Regarding that matter, it is with great difficulty that I
report... After their defeat, it seems they have vanished."

Demon Lord \N[33]: "What did you say...?! For someone who is one of the
three generals..."
Demon Lord \N[33]: "Hmph... Well, no matter, I have no use for losers!"

Demon Lord \N[33]: "The gate will open shortly... \N[33], you must
absolutely defeat the Warriors of Light! Understand?! Ah-ha-ha-ha."
